methods.console:
Creates a new console session of script type type.

 
 Note: the server does not currently support independent console sessions. See
 Issue 1172.

:param type: (java.lang.String) - the script type
:return: (java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<? extends io.deephaven.client.impl.ConsoleSession>) the console session future
methods.publish:
Publishes ticket into the global scope with name.

:param name: (java.lang.String) - the name, must conform to SourceVersion.isName(CharSequence)
:param ticketId: (io.deephaven.client.impl.HasTicketId) - the export ID
:return: (java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.lang.Void>) the publish completable future
